---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { roofingAsphalt, ctaAssistant } from '../../../lib/images';
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../../../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';
import Navbar from '../../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Hero from '../../../components/Hero.astro';
import LogoSlider from '../../../components/LogoSlider.astro';
import FAQ from '../../../components/FAQ.astro';
import ContactUs from '../../../components/ContactUs.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';

const city = 'Novato';
const county = 'Marin County';
const adjective = 'Affordable';
---

<Layout
  title={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA | Hamilton Exteriors`}
  description={`Hamilton Exteriors provides ${adjective.toLowerCase()} ADU contractors in ${city}, CA. Expert design, permits, and construction. Call for a free consultation!`}
>
  <AnnouncementBar />
  <Navbar />
  <Hero
    formTitle={`Get a FREE Estimate in ${city}`}
    headline={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA`}
  />
  <LogoSlider />

  <!-- Why Choose Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-white py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={roofingAsphalt} alt="Hamilton Exteriors ADU project" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/478;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why Choose Hamilton Exteriors as Your {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Budget-Friendly. Reliable. Smart.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Hamilton Exteriors provides affordable ADU contractors in Novato, CA who prove that quality construction doesn't have to break the bank. Novato is Marin County's largest city by area, with spacious lots in neighborhoods like Indian Valley, Pacheco Valle, and Hamilton that are well-suited for ADU projects. Our team delivers solid construction at competitive prices, making ADU ownership accessible to more Novato homeowners.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Affordable doesn't mean cheap. We achieve competitive pricing through efficient project management, strong supplier relationships, and streamlined construction processes — not by cutting corners on materials or workmanship. Every Novato ADU we build meets the same quality standards as our premium projects, just without the unnecessary markups.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We help Novato homeowners understand the true cost of an ADU build upfront, explore financing options, and make smart choices about features and finishes that maximize value within their budget. With $0 down financing available, getting started is easier than you might think.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Competitive Pricing</strong> — We provide honest, detailed estimates that reflect fair market rates for quality ADU construction, with no inflated margins or hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Full Permit Handling</strong> — We manage all city permits and inspections, avoiding the costly mistakes that come from homeowners trying to navigate the complex process themselves.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Quality Materials</strong> — Premium construction materials selected for durability, energy efficiency, and long-term value that stand up to the Bay Area's unique climate conditions.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Flexible Financing</strong> — $0 down financing options make it easy to start your ADU project without a large upfront investment, making homeownership more accessible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why ADU Contractors Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-cream py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA Are Essential?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Value. Access. Opportunity.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Novato offers some of Marin County's most accessible entry points for homeownership, but even here, property prices are significant. An ADU is one of the smartest financial moves a Novato homeowner can make — it generates rental income in a county with extremely high rents, provides flexible space for family members, and increases your property's appraised value substantially.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Affordable contractors are essential in Novato because the cost of construction in Marin County can quickly escalate beyond what many homeowners can justify. Without an affordable option, many Novato families who would benefit most from an ADU — those looking for multigenerational housing solutions or supplemental income — are priced out of the market entirely. An affordable contractor opens the door to these benefits.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
        With affordable ADU contractors, you get access to professional design, permitting, and construction services at a price point that makes the project financially worthwhile — turning your Novato property into a more valuable, more versatile asset for your family.
      </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={ctaAssistant} alt="Hamilton Exteriors construction crew" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/626;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <FAQ />
  <ContactUs />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
